@startuml 02_AuthenticationFlow
participant User
participant Controller
participant AuthService
participant Database

User -> Controller: POST /auth/login
activate Controller
Controller -> AuthService: validateCredentials(username, password)
activate AuthService

AuthService -> Database: SELECT user WHERE username=?
activate Database
Database --> AuthService: user record
deactivate Database

AuthService -> AuthService: bcrypt.compare(password, hash)
note right: Verify password hash

AuthService --> Controller: JWT token
deactivate AuthService

Controller --> User: 200 OK with token
deactivate Controller

note over User: Client stores JWT in Authorization header

User -> Controller: GET /projects
activate Controller
note right: Authorization: Bearer <token>

Controller -> Controller: validateToken()
note right: Verify signature and expiration

Controller -> Database: SELECT role FROM users WHERE id=?
activate Database
Database --> Controller: role from DB
deactivate Database
note right: Always re-fetch role from DB

Controller --> User: 200 OK with data
deactivate Controller

@enduml
